metadata.name: Dimensional IX: Whimsy #1/9
metadata.description:
There is nothing more whimsy than you being in the world with me.

I’m glad you’re here, sharing this moment underneath the world tree.

Dedicated to those who see, and read this image. I’m grateful you shared this moment with me. Thank you for being in the world.


Collaboration between Jerad Armijo (Away I flew) and Amaurie Ramirez
